---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ContactButton from "../components/ContactButton.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="container mx-auto p-4 pt-30">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-ebony mb-8 text-center">Our Services</h1>
      
      <!-- Manual Testing -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 text-red-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ebony">Manual Testing</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-ebony leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Comprehensive manual testing services to ensure your software meets the highest quality standards. 
          Our expert testers meticulously examine every aspect of your application to identify potential issues 
          before they reach your users.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ebony mb-2">Functional Testing</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• User interface testing</li>
              <li>• Business logic validation</li>
              <li>• Cross-browser compatibility</li>
              <li>• Mobile responsiveness</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ebony mb-2">Usability Testing</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• User experience evaluation</li>
              <li>• Accessibility compliance</li>
              <li>• Performance assessment</li>
              <li>• User flow optimization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Automated Testing -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 text-red-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ebony">Automated Testing</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-ebony leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Streamline your testing process with our automated testing solutions. We implement robust automation 
          frameworks that increase efficiency, reduce testing time, and provide consistent results across all 
          your software releases.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ebony mb-2">Framework Implementation</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Selenium WebDriver</li>
              <li>• Playwright</li>
              <li>• Custom framework development</li>
              <li>• CI/CD integration</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ebony mb-2">Automation Services</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Test script development</li>
              <li>• Maintenance and updates</li>
              <li>• Performance testing</li>
              <li>• API testing automation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quality Assurance -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 text-red-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ebony">Quality Assurance</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-ebony leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Comprehensive quality assurance services to ensure your software meets industry standards and 
          exceeds user expectations. We implement best practices and methodologies to maintain the highest 
          quality throughout the development lifecycle.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ebony mb-2">QA Processes</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Test planning and strategy</li>
              <li>• Risk assessment</li>
              <li>• Quality metrics tracking</li>
              <li>• Process improvement</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ebony mb-2">Documentation</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Test case development</li>
              <li>• Bug reporting</li>
              <li>• Test documentation</li>
              <li>• Quality reports</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Consulting -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 text-red-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ebony">Consulting</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-ebony leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Expert consulting services to help you optimize your testing processes and implement best practices 
          in quality assurance. We provide guidance and support to enhance your team's capabilities and 
          improve your software quality.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ebony mb-2">Process Optimization</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Testing methodology review</li>
              <li>• Tool selection</li>
              <li>• Team training</li>
              <li>• Best practices implementation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ebony mb-2">Strategic Planning</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Quality roadmap development</li>
              <li>• Resource planning</li>
              <li>• Risk management</li>
              <li>• Performance optimization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
